qFoldIT distributes this code under the terms of the Apache License 2.0
(see LICENSE). As of this notice, the server code (src/, tests/, Dockerfiles,
pyproject.toml) is substantially unmodified from upstream, WITH ONE
DOCUMENTED EXCEPTION (below) -- installation instructions in README.md
still correctly point to the upstream project's own PyPI package,
container registry, and source repository for everything else, since
